title: Lenovo ThinkPad SL410/510/500
description:
This is a stock factory restore set ripped directly from source for the Lenovo ThinkPad SL410.

OS: Windows 7 Pro 64bit Service Pack 1

Also restores on the following Lenovo/IBM ThinkPads:

ThinkPad SL510
ThinkPad SL500
ThinkPad T400
ThinkPad T500

Activates without any hacks or cracks on the above Lenovo hardware. May work on other Lenovo systems. I've had bad luck with anything older than a T400.

Hope this helps any of you out there who didn't burn a recovery set for your Lenovo before a hardware or software failure.
